{"1340480":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood","steam_appid":1340480,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[2554890,2554900],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood is a thought-provoking narrative experience from the creators of The Red Strings Club. Featuring a richly diverse cast of characters, Tarot-like card creation, divination, and a branching story that spans time and space, The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood explores themes of identity, community, and personal responsibility in a beautifully hand-crafted universe. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Fortuna, a Witch living exiled on an asteroid who forms a pact with a forbidden creature in the hopes of regaining her freedom. Reconnect with your Witch friends after a 200-year-long exile, meet new Witches, and use the cards you created to pierce through their pasts and futures. As you delve into this universe, you will see yourself immersed in the complex web of interests that surround your coven, leading to a political plot that will define the fate of the Cosmic Witch society. <\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spellbinding Story <\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a complex narrative spanning decades as Fortuna comes to terms with her power and the impact her decisions have on others and the fate of her Coven. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcane Deck Building<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft unique divination cards from hundreds of possibilities to help you understand and determine the fate of the characters you encounter. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Magical Music<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 3 hours of bewitching original music by the celebrated composer fingerspit. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enchanting Visuals <\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Savour the stunning hand-crafted pixel art visuals and a huge cast of deliciously designed witches from all walks of life.<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood is a thought-provoking narrative experience from the creators of The Red Strings Club. Featuring a richly diverse cast of characters, Tarot-like card creation, divination, and a branching story that spans time and space, The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood explores themes of identity, community, and personal responsibility in a beautifully hand-crafted universe. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Fortuna, a Witch living exiled on an asteroid who forms a pact with a forbidden creature in the hopes of regaining her freedom. Reconnect with your Witch friends after a 200-year-long exile, meet new Witches, and use the cards you created to pierce through their pasts and futures. As you delve into this universe, you will see yourself immersed in the complex web of interests that surround your coven, leading to a political plot that will define the fate of the Cosmic Witch society. <\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spellbinding Story <\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a complex narrative spanning decades as Fortuna comes to terms with her power and the impact her decisions have on others and the fate of her Coven. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/739ec349c301a5e91d633c8a26949a6a.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcane Deck Building<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft unique divination cards from hundreds of possibilities to help you understand and determine the fate of the characters you encounter. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/6c7bb07d9adae3a1818e57c4f878cda0.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Magical Music<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 3 hours of bewitching original music by the celebrated composer fingerspit. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/extras\/4c5dda601592f33e9014c27240abe383.mp4?t=1765878706\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enchanting Visuals <\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Savour the stunning hand-crafted pixel art visuals and a huge cast of deliciously designed witches from all walks of life.<\/p>","short_description":"Immerse yourself in an enchanting narrative experience as Fortuna, a fortune-teller Witch condemned to exile on her asteroid home. Craft your own Tarot deck, regain your freedom, and shape the fate of the cosmic Witch society.","supported_languages":"English, French, Spanish - Spain, Japanese, Russian, Simplified Chinese, German","reviews":"“a masterwork of narrative and character, positing impactful questions”<br>5\/5 – GamesRadar<br><br>“another engrossing exploration of choice and consequence”<br>4.5\/5 – ScreenRant<br><br>“The story is engrossing, the art is terrific, and the emotional impact is undeniable.”<br>9\/10 – COGconnected<br>","header_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/header.jpg?t=1765878706","capsule_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1765878706","capsule_imagev5":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1340480\/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1765878706","website":"https:\/\/www.cosmicwheelsisterhood.com\/","pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br><\/li><li><strong>OS:<\/strong> Windows 7x64<br><\/li><li><strong>Processor:<\/strong> Intel Core i3-3240; AMD A10-5800K<br><\/li><li><strong>Memory:<\/strong> 8 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>Graphics:<\/strong> GeForce GT 640; Radeon HD 7750; Intel HD Graphics 515<br><\/li><li><strong>DirectX:<\/strong> Version 11<br><\/li><li><strong>Storage:<\/strong> 1 GB available space<\/li><\/ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br><\/li><li><strong>OS:<\/strong> Windows 10 x64<br><\/li><li><strong>Processor:<\/strong> Intel Core i3-4160; AMD FX-4350<br><\/li><li><strong>Memory:<\/strong> 8 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>Graphics:<\/strong> GeForce GTX 650; Radeon HD 7770; Intel Iris Pro Graphics 580<br><\/li><li><strong>DirectX:<\/strong> Version 11<br><\/li><li><